<table>MI.BUDGET.CONTROL</table>
</header>
<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>This file is used to create the MI.BUDGET.LINE records which in turn create the MI.BUDGET reocrds which the MI databases uses as its source of budget information. Verfication of this record will create a record on the unauthorised file of MI.BUDGET.LINE with a key determined by the contents of the MI.BUDGET.CONTROL record. </p>
            <p>The record will be in hold status. </p>
            <p>If a record already exists on either the live or the unauthorised file then the information held on those records will be copied to the new record, along with any new itmes. </p>
        </ovdesc>
<ovimage></ovimage>
</overview>
